    "description":  "Information for candidates applying for the Lawyer vacancies in the Advisory Divisions, Commercial Law Group, Employment Group and Litigation Group ",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"headline-information\"\u003eHeadline Information\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eDepartment\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eGovernment Legal Department\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eDivision\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eAdvisory, Commercial, Employment and Litigation\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eJob title\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eLawyer\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eLocation\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eLondon\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eSalary\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eGrade 7- £48,800 (London), Legal Officer - £42,844 (up to 3 years \u003cabbr title=\"Post Qualification Experience\"\u003ePQE\u003c/abbr\u003e)\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"vacancy-details\"\u003eVacancy details\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/government-legal-department\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eGovernment Legal Department (\u003cabbr title=\"Government Legal Department\"\u003eGLD\u003c/abbr\u003e)\u003c/a\u003e is the largest provider of legal services across government, working with all the main Whitehall departments. From roads to rivers, and health to human rights, our work touches on most aspects of public life.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe are a non-ministerial government department with more than 2,500 employees, around 1,800 of whom are solicitors or barristers. The department is based primarily in London but has teams in Bristol, Manchester, and Leeds.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe are looking for highly capable qualified lawyers to join our supportive teams where we can offer a challenging and exciting career.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhether you join us as an advisory, employment, commercial or litigation lawyer, we offer broad and unrivalled career opportunities.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe would be thrilled to receive applications from candidates whatever stage you are at in your legal career. Whether you are newly qualified, returning to work after a break, or looking to ‘do something different’, \u003cabbr title=\"Government Legal Department\"\u003eGLD\u003c/abbr\u003e is a supportive and happy place to work.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThese posts are London based only.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"apply\"\u003eApply\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFor further information on the post and details on how to apply, please visit \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.gld-qualified.co.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003e\u003cabbr title=\"Government Legal Department\"\u003eGLD\u003c/abbr\u003e’s Recruitment Website.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e",
